@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dmpnsk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.77
    v2 = 0.62
    v1 = (0.63 - tmp)
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.43) / wp.cos(tmp))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.69) / v2) + tmp)
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v1 + 0.47 + v0 + 0.38)))
    data[tid] = v0
